### Youyu — Admin Panel
### Run this file after every change to admin endpoints.
### Prerequisite: backend started with -Dspring-boot.run.profiles=seed

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@adminToken = mock-9001-ADMIN
@superAdminToken = mock-9101-SUPER_ADMIN
@supportToken = mock-9102-SUPPORT_AGENT
@reviewerToken = mock-9103-REVIEWER
@operatorToken = mock-9104-OPERATOR
@orderAdminToken = mock-9105-ORDER_ADMIN
@userToken = mock-1001-USER

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# AUTH GUARD
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### Admin endpoint with USER token → expect 403
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

###

### Admin endpoint with no token → expect 401
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/dashboard

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# DASHBOARD
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────

###

### Dashboard overview
### Expected data fields:
### - summary
### - queueMetrics[] with stable id/source/target/available fields
### - governanceSignals[]
### - statusBreakdowns.orders[] and statusBreakdowns.mediation[]
### - salesAnalytics.categorySales[] and salesAnalytics.shopRankings[]
### - unavailableMetrics[] for non-instrumented metrics
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# USER MANAGEMENT
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────

###

### List all users — page 1, size 10
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### List users — filter active, page 1
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users?status=active&page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### List users — keyword search, page 1
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users?keyword=张&page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### User detail
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users/1001
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Disable user
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users/1003/status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "disabled",
  "restrictionReason": "测试禁用"
}

###

### Re-enable user
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users/1003/status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "active",
  "restrictionReason": ""
}

###

### Reject unsupported user status - expect 400 BAD_REQUEST
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users/1003/status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "suspended"
}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# STUDENT VERIFICATION
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────

###

### List all verifications — page 1, size 10
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/verifications?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### List verifications — pending only
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/verifications?status=pending_review&page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Approve verification
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/verifications/2002/review
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "approve",
  "reviewNote": "信息核实通过"
}

###

### Reject verification — missing rejectReason → expect 400
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/verifications/2002/review
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "reject"
}

###

### Reject verification — with reason
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/verifications/2003/review
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "reject",
  "rejectReason": "学号与实名信息不一致",
  "reviewNote": "请补充有效校园身份证明"
}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# PRODUCT MANAGEMENT
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────

###

### List all products — page 1, size 10
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/products?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### List products — pending review only
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/products?reviewStatus=pending_review&page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### List products — digital type
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/products?productType=digital&page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Reject unsupported product status - expect 400 BAD_REQUEST
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/products/3010/status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "shadow_hidden"
}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# REVIEW TASKS
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────

###

### List all review tasks — page 1, size 10
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/review-tasks?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### List review tasks — pending
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/review-tasks?status=pending_review&page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Approve review task
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/review-tasks/5001/review
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "approve",
  "reviewNote": "资料内容合规，可上架"
}

###

### Reject review task
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/review-tasks/5001/review
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "reject",
  "rejectReason": "资料来源不清晰",
  "reviewNote": "请补充原创或授权说明"
}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# SHOP MANAGEMENT
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────

###

### List all shops — page 1, size 10
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/shops?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### List shops — pending review
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/shops?reviewStatus=pending_review&page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Shop detail
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/shops/4001
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Approve shop
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/shops/4002/status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "active",
  "reviewStatus": "approved"
}

###

### Reject invalid shop status/reviewStatus combination - expect 400 BAD_REQUEST
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/shops/4003/status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "disabled",
  "reviewStatus": "approved"
}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# REPORT MANAGEMENT
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────

###

### List all reports — page 1, size 10
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/reports?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### List reports — pending
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/reports?status=pending&page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Process report — move to resolved
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/reports/6001/process
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "resolved",
  "resolution": "已核实并通知相关用户"
}

###

### Process report — missing status → expect 400
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/reports/6001/process
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

###

### Process report with unsupported status - expect 400 BAD_REQUEST
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/reports/6001/process
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "ignored",
  "resolution": "invalid status smoke"
}

###

### Escalate eligible order report to mediation
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/reports/6010/escalate-to-mediation
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "escalationReason": "Order-backed dispute requires formal mediation."
}

###

### Escalate non-order report to mediation - expect 400 BAD_REQUEST
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/reports/6001/escalate-to-mediation
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

###

### List mediation cases
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/mediation-cases?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### List mediation cases by status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/mediation-cases?status=evidence_review&page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Mediation case detail
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/mediation-cases/70001
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Mediation status update
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/mediation-cases/70001/status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "decision_pending"
}

###

### Mediation final decision
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/mediation-cases/70001/decision
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "decisionCategory": "order_completion_required",
  "decisionSummary": "Evidence review supports order completion.",
  "enforcementSummary": "Order module remains the owner of operational state."
}

# ADMIN BATCH OPERATIONS

###

### Review task detail for admin drawer
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/review-tasks/5001
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Batch update user status
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users/batch-status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ids": [1002],
  "status": "active",
  "restrictionReason": ""
}

###

### Batch review student verifications
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/verifications/batch-review
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ids": [2002],
  "action": "approve",
  "reviewNote": "Batch smoke approve"
}

###

### Batch update product status
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/products/batch-status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ids": [3010],
  "status": "off_sale"
}

###

### Batch review product tasks
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/review-tasks/batch-review
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ids": [5001],
  "action": "approve",
  "reviewNote": "Batch smoke approve"
}

###

### Batch update shop status
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/shops/batch-status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ids": [4003],
  "status": "active",
  "reviewStatus": "approved"
}

###

### Batch process reports
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/reports/batch-process
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ids": [6001],
  "status": "processing",
  "resolution": "Batch smoke processing"
}

# AUDIT LOGS

###

### List admin audit logs
### Expected item fields:
### - operatorUserId, operatorRole, action, targetType, targetId, summary, createdAt
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/audit-logs?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### List audit logs for user status changes
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/audit-logs?action=USER_STATUS_UPDATE&targetType=USER&page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Audit logs with USER token - expect 403
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/audit-logs
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

# ROLE PERMISSION SMOKE

###

### Reviewer can access verification queue
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/verifications?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{reviewerToken}}

###

### Reviewer cannot access order admin queue - expect 403
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{reviewerToken}}

###

### Operator can access search governance
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/search/governance-rules
Authorization: Bearer {{operatorToken}}

###

### Support agent cannot record final mediation decisions - expect 403
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/mediation-cases/70001/decision
Authorization: Bearer {{supportToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "decisionCategory": "order_completion_required",
  "decisionSummary": "Permission smoke should be rejected."
}

###

### Order admin can access order queue
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{orderAdminToken}}

# SUPPORT TICKETS

###

### Support agent can list support tickets
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/support/tickets?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{supportToken}}

###

### Support agent can filter support tickets
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/support/tickets?status=open&category=order&assignedToMe=false&page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{supportToken}}

###

### Admin support ticket detail includes public replies and internal notes
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/support/tickets/6201
Authorization: Bearer {{supportToken}}

###

### Support agent changes support ticket status and assigns to self
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/support/tickets/6201/status
Authorization: Bearer {{supportToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "in_progress",
  "assignToMe": true
}

###

### Support agent adds public ticket reply
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/support/tickets/6201/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{supportToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "messageType": "public_reply",
  "content": "We are checking the platform context for this support ticket."
}

###

### Support agent adds internal note
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/support/tickets/6201/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{supportToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "messageType": "internal_note",
  "content": "Context note only. Do not mutate order, report, mediation, or chat state from support."
}

###

### User cannot access admin support ticket queue - expect 403
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/support/tickets
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
